net.proteusframework.ui.miwt

Interface ApplicationFactory


  • public interface ApplicationFactory
    Defines an interface to create MIWTApplication instances. Implementations may optionally provide a more complex way to create application instances apart from the default behavior of using the application constructor.
    Author:
    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com)
